  "description": "Dive into a dark fantasy world where every fallen monster could drop powerful, legendary weapons, turning each battle into a thrilling treasure hunt.",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/5XPGp2GQ/Unique-Loot-Curseforge-Icon.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"100\"><div style=\"border:3px solid #fa0707\"><p style=\"color:#fa0707;font-size:1.7em;text-align:center\"><strong>Unique Loot</strong></p><p style=\"color:#fff;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>Dive into a dark fantasy world where</strong> <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>every fallen monster</strong></span> <strong>could drop powerful, legendary weapons</strong>, turning each battle into a <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>thrilling treasure hunt</strong></span>.</p><p style=\"color:#fff;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>With</strong> <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>Unique Loot</strong></span>, <strong>your combat experience evolves, adding an exhilarating twist to every showdown and making each encounter a dramatic opportunity to become more powerful.</strong></p><p style=\"color:#fa0707;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>Perfect for players who want a dark, rewarding, and dynamic twist to their Minecraft adventure.</strong></p><p style=\"color:#fff;font-size:1.5em;text-align:center\"><strong>How it works?</strong><br>The mod changes the sword skin with a the name of a resource pack skin, in this case (<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/vanity-fantasy-3d-weapons\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fantasy 3D Weapons by Nongko</a>) (Download Required). It has a <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>config.json</strong></span> file in case you want to add yours! It has a <span style=\"color:#fa0707\"><strong>0.20%</strong></span> probability of dropping a unique sword, with a random name and stats, so prepare to kill enemies and gain unique loot!</p></div><p><br></p><div style=\"text-align:center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/4gytaRTKuc\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/bBpJOKO.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"> </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_d_4.v_1_d_/\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/YHadOI4.png\" alt=\"Instagram\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"> </a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <a href=\"http://twitch.tv/p1as0p\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"text-decoration:none\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/URFEihO.png\" alt=\"Twitch\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"></a></div><p><br><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/modpacks/pingaland\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RVaO5gj.png\" alt=\"Play Pingaland\" width=\"1280\" height=\"507\"></a></p></div>",
